'desc': [u'

Nuby Bath Tub (Yellow) Price: Rs.450

Bathing your baby at home with no one’s help can be a bit of a task. Holding your infant’s wobbly body and giving her a proper bath is not that easy. The Nuby Bath Tub is a perfect accessory that allows you to single handedly bathe your little angel in your own bath tub. This specially designed Bath Tub from Nuby has a contour that gives proper support to your tiny tot’s body and helps you in bathing the child effortlessly.

The durable plastic with which the Nuby Contour Bath Tub is made can be cleaned easily. The suction cups at the base of the Bath Tub offers a reliable grip to the Nuby tub and helps in keeping it in place when your baby is seated in it. With this Nuby Tub you can make sure that your bundle of joy gets the safest bath experience with you
